, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=579215\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579215\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-19-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with green and white vertical striped tiles, a glass shower enclosure, wall-mounted showerhead, sink with black fixtures, and shelves holding towels and toiletries.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-19-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-19-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEven the communal spaces make a statement. On the ground floor, green and orange hues meet durable natural rubber flooring from Nora, while the upper levels feature a patchwork of \u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/tag/ege-carpets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eEGE Carpets\u003c/a\u003e – both plain and patterned. A vintage suspension light and \u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/tag/foscarini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eFoscarini’s\u003c/a\u003e sculptural Bits sconces help set the tone as guests enter.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=579216\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579216\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-20-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern building lobby with green tiled steps, blue tiled walls, a blue elevator, and contemporary ceiling light fixture.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-20-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-20-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-20-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=579217\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579217\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-21-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Brightly lit interior with colorful wall lamps, blue and brown tiled surfaces, green flooring, and an elevator door on the left.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-21-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-21-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Montmontre-Tourist-Apartments-Paris-Hoch-Chho-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=579218\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579218\" 